{"data":{"page":{"id":"394a2eaa-20f8-5158-8b83-542757cf7f7c","html":"<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/12567686669ff460c311c0d0964cb731/877ff/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/12567686669ff460c311c0d0964cb731/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/12567686669ff460c311c0d0964cb731/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/12567686669ff460c311c0d0964cb731/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>During my travels around Asia, I met Germán, a Colombian photographer with a special love for India and Korea. We met in Fukuoka, Japan and we exchanged travel experiences while drinking some Japanese tea. A few months later, I decided to build a Wordpress website for him with a photo gallery for his work.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"2010"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Germán Linares","categories":"web wordpress inverted","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/f54701df3053256c552279c6d3a48d9f/445d9/logo.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/german-linares/","source":"work"}}